                    "body": "Not sure what happened to the original person who reported this, but this doesn't appear to be fixed in 1.6.2\n\nIf you specify a translator via Zend_Form using setDefaultTranslator, the translator is still null when processed by Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract.php so the error message is not being translated.",
